item.title: This One Move Will Make You Dance Like Blackpink in 'How You Like That'!
item.description: Introduction Are you a fan of the K-Pop girl group Blackpink and their hit song “How You Like That”? If so, you may be wondering how you can dance like the members of Blackpink in the song Well, we’ve got some great news for you! We’ve discovered one move that, when mastered, will make you dance like Blackpink in no time! Overview of Blackpink’s Song “How You Like That” Blackpink’s “How You Like That” is a high-energy song that features a catchy hook and a powerful beat.
